Sherihan (amụrụ na 6 Disemba 1964) bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe , onye na-agụ egwu na onye na-agba egwú.
Sherihan malitere ime ihe nkiri mgbe ọ dị afọ anọ. A maara ya nke ọma maka Fawazir Ramadan
Ọ lara ezumike nká n'afọ 2002 wee pụọ n'ọrụ n'afọ 2016. N'afọ 2021, ọ laghachiri n'ọkwa ya mgbe afọ 20 nke ime ihe nkiri site na ime ihe nkiri na Coco Chanel.
Sherihan bụ nwanne nwanyị Omar Khorshid. Ọ lụrụ onye ọchụnta ego Jọdan Alaa Khawaja, onye ya na ya nwere ụmụ nwanyị abụọ.
N'afọ 1990, o nwere nnukwu ihe mberede, ebe ọ gbajiri azụ ya nakwa ọkpụkpụ azụ. N'afọ 2002, ọ rịara ọrịa akpịrị akpịrị akpị, nke mere ka ọ kwụsị ọrụ ime ihe nkiri.
Sherihan bụkwa onye mba Ijipt a ma ama ma bụrụkwa onye isi na-ekere òkè na mgbanwe nke ala nna ya na 2011 na-achọ iwepụ onye isi ala Hosni Mubarak.
